des:
SAKI Smart products help you control home appliances. You can simply ask Alexa to control your smart home device.

After connecting Alexa to your SAKI Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "SAKI Smart" app in the android or ios app market;
(2). Register one account in our "SAKI Smart" app;
(3). You need to have some SAKI Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "SAKI Smart" app and change the appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "SAKI Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "SAKI Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "SAKI Smart", and you'll be navigated to the "SAKI Smart" login page;
(9). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on air purifier.”
“Alexa, turn off air purifier.”
